Classification: Scripted
Genre: Comedy
Status: Returning Series
Network: BBC One ( United Kingdom)
Airs: Mondays at 10:35 pm
Runtime: 30 Minutes
Premiere: February 21, 2011

Mrs Brown's Boys is a comedy series which stars Brendan O'Carroll as Agnes Brown. Agnes is a funny, foul-mouthed Dublin mother who interferes in the lives of her children and friends.
